Package data

Interface Summary
XmlCompatible Contains converting method to XML format.
 

Class Summary
Arc Contains features of the arc of petri-net, Provides methods for setting and getting this features.
Data Main data storage of the application, It contains all visible Elements, active Element, added Element, commandStack and flag of chaning.
Element Abstract class for all Elements of petri-net, It provides all base and general abilities and features for all type of Elements.
ElementSimpleFactory Generate new Element from XML file tag.
ElementXmlParser Parses XML file to Data object.
Generator Contains method of generation of time transition if it works.
Place Contains features of the place of petri-net, Provides methods for setting and getting this features.
TableManagment Provides different operations with data, like making Di/Dq/Dr matrix and marking line.
Transition Contains features of the transition of petri-net, Provides methods for setting and getting this features.
